Output assets/cru-overview.gif

Require cru

Set Shell "bash"
Set FontSize 18
Set Width 960
Set Height 540
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set WindowBar Colorful
Set WindowBarSize 40
Set Padding 24
Set TypingSpeed 40ms

Type "cru --version && cru stats -C assets/demo-config.toml --no-process"
Enter
Sleep 5s
